name: Ultimate-Feel Haiku
description:
Haiku is traditionally Minimalist Japanese poetry.
That originated in The 9th Century.

A haiku is more than a type of poem;
It is a way of looking at the physical world and seeing something more profound,
Like the very nature of existence.
"It should leave the reader with a strong feeling or impression."

"Ultimate-Feel Haiku"
